description: These pizza baguettes are simple to make and delicious.
keywords: Meat pizza,Soy free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Turkey,Sesame free,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Turkey Pizza Baguette Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 medium red onion, peeled and diced

recipeInstructions.text: Pre-heat the oven to 180°C/160°C fan-forced. Chop the cooked turkey into bite size pieces.
On your sliced baguettes, spread the tomato paste, then the cheese and then the rest of the ingredients.
Bake the pizza baguettes in the oven for 10 minutes or until the bread is slightly toasted on the sides.
